Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:45.56,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}紧握决意抵在左胸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:50.35,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}劈裂「愚行之螺旋」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:53.90,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}翱翔于苍穹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:59.24,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自由之翼
